{"tid":2104204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"讓本土派成為主流？ 睇完呢幅圖真係得啖笑","createTime":"2020-07-11T18:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T20:35:26.000Z","uid":11971,"like":13,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"71a452087cd93853da5d0885ce6c6d3412f6f309","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/On5k2cx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOn5k2cx.jpg&h=3fa41418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每區剩係谷一個本土派出嚟<br />\n而家直選議席非建制派諗住出23席<br />\n你哋班人就係推5個本土派出去就算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當其他本土派係咩？<br />\n咁樣俾人帶風向法真係俾呢5個入咗去立法會有幾大影響力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKhSTkf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKhSTkf.png&h=2c388683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我用新西做例子<br />\n假設張可森好順利咁俾大家谷咗入去<br />\n之後朱凱迪郭家麒尹兆堅呢啲有鐵票基本上十拿九穩<br />\n好啦咁剩低呢<br />\n吳敏兒係主張工會戰線稱唔上本土派<br />\n咁剩低3個伍健偉 譚凱邦 黃子悦佢哋3個本土派爭一個名額？<br />\n<br />\n大家眼見啲票站中年老年人居多<br />\n佢哋大部分都係會投翻傳統泛民<br />\n投本土派嘅又未必完全了解所有甚至係有邊個係本土派<br />\n又如何讓本土派成為主流呢？<br />\n<br />\n要贏唔單止建制要輸 係泛民都要輸 俾佢哋知道而家嘅政治環境係要淘汰呢班泛民"},{"pid":"696fa82106ae195fffc2e38fb79f298f899d3f9c","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJfdCRr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJfdCRr.jpg&h=a1dc01d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我再用呢幅圖做例子<br />\n但係我唔係針對王百羽同埋圖入面所有人<br />\n大家話我分化都好<br />\n我眼見琴日嘅拉票主要係互相最想谷個幾個本土派<br />\n某程度上佢哋係一個圈子<br />\n起碼以上人名入面我唔見天水圍連線嘅人<br />\n大佬大家都係本土派冇必要再細分<br />\n剩係谷自己圈子嘅人就得？"},{"pid":"9a593a041bbbcad39ab32d3beac38336cf8b885c","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:49:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e37b4cf6fc96763a4fa09c96689c1a0a37f7a27","tid":2104204,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afa121bbea254deaba59c00160498f2787f910c5","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87fe651379ab9b12143d967a74a7c00068823f6f","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:52:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cd48c0a6fc1ceb2490adf3146983a684086b599","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:53:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19cca0d2e214744a37dfc644050051ea01c28594","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgftrNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgftrNY.jpg&h=764fb7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至少都推哂呢班人入去先<br />\n得5個入去？唔好講笑啦大佬"},{"pid":"4ed7480bb17be16abc84c9317300e6835a26f223","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:56:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31fe16d101462c28f68fc8098fcd73ab5bede830","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:57:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a784b6eb9a5e1b89108f30a790857a6f90aa73c8","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:58:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cc57f94e3e73903a4ebdeb6be474fd9af034948","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:58:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52d78e011c205bfd8f55cbddb7196dc20b05607e","tid":2104204,"uid":12185,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:59:16.000Z","msg":"都要睇實際情況架大佬<br />\n你估區區都可以好似新東咁夠票容納到兩席或以上嘅本土咩<br />\n喺度嘈有咩用"},{"pid":"81c7aa7561f684966c34eb4b974d662f3d8d76c3","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:59:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c574e575dca60251791e47135f2f804cbd0