"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgftrNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgftrNY.jpg&h=764fb7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至少都推哂呢班人入去先<br />\n得5個入去？唔好講笑啦大佬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T19:30:10.000Z","msg":"不如搵埋黃台仰返黎呀笨<br />\n推推推 推撚到先得架"},{"pid":"097534b5fceb4b2bf097e09c3b387e59d0c031a2","tid":2104204,"uid":137078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696fa82106ae195fffc2e38fb79f298f899d3f9c","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJfdCRr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJfdCRr.jpg&h=a1dc01d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我再用呢幅圖做例子<br />\n但係我唔係針對王百羽同埋圖入面所有人<br />\n大家話我分化都好<br />\n我眼見琴日嘅拉票主要係互相最想谷個幾個本土派<br />\n某程度上佢哋係一個圈子<br />\n起碼以上人名入面我唔見天水圍連線嘅人<br />\n大佬大家都係本土派冇必要再細分<br />\n剩係谷自己圈子嘅人就得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T19:32:11.000Z","msg":"認真本土票源唔穩<br />\n而佢谷個啲一個都唔識<br />\n好流於連登/Fb<br />\n<br />\n我知有街站/初選<br />\n但當初選街站投票人以中老年為主（6成以上）可能小弟睇錯<br />\n實際本土比較輸蝕<br />\n就算後生票可能都去咗相對較高知名度嘅眾志度<br />\n如果我係中年人，間中睇吓新聞，本土我有機識天水連線，反而眾志仲會識多啲<br />\n我諗傳統泛民票會比比連登仔想像多"},{"pid":"31a9b38be1a166f00a02d0c2077e16ad226abd7b","tid":2104204,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T19:39:37.000Z","msg":"無人諗下點樣𠝹/搶藍絲票<br />\n但就一日幾百個post諗傳統泛民/本土點互𠝹比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5621547b86c40c3827cd9901ef7b7df090c1b6f4","tid":2104204,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a9b38be1a166f00a02d0c2077e16ad226abd7b","tid":2104204,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T19:39:37.000Z","msg":"無人諗下點樣𠝹/搶藍絲票<br />\n但就一日幾百個post諗傳統泛民/本土點互𠝹比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T19:49:47.000Z","msg":"初選本土唔夠泛民票就冇得玩<br />\n仲點𠝹法?"}],"pinned":{"pid":"19cca0d2e214744a37dfc644050051ea01c28594","tid":2104204,"uid":11971,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgftrNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgftrNY.jpg&h=764fb7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至少都推哂呢班人入去先<br />\n得5個入去？唔好講笑啦大佬"}}